{"tid":2213842,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：沒病癥的人幾乎沒有傳播新冠病毒的能力；特朗普：中共錯誤聲稱沒病徵的人不會傳播病毒，必須負責。","createTime":"2020-09-23T00:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T23:06:55.000Z","uid":271829,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2a70b6e2c84221504957d435ae3980612b78ff10","tid":2213842,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:01:35.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n陳雲：祖國大陸的醫學發現，香港政府要聽嗎？中國研究人員在廣州的研究發現，沒病癥的人幾乎沒有傳播新冠病毒的能力，故此無限期玩封城罷課限聚令口罩令，以「堵截傳播鏈」為理由而推行限制是毫無醫學根據的。<br />\n...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G0CYKuk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG0CYKuk.png&h=1ecf4c59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n特朗普指責中國政府，實際控制世界衛生組織，錯誤聲稱沒有證據顯示新型肺炎可人傳人，又錯誤聲稱沒有病徵的人不會傳播病毒，聯合國必須要中國負責。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551068-20200922.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551068-20200922.htm&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I24L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=dfe611a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551068-20200922.htm&h=8c23edf8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551068-20200922.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bc76b9b49c64ed8cb0ab1913801df6d55ae14d0a","tid":2213842,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T23:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死廢老"}]}